{"tid":2425413,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 其實孟達係抵撚死唔抵可憐，你班偽道德撚收皮啦","createTime":"2021-02-27T10:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T09:19:17.000Z","uid":52658,"like":175,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ce73bb994a83e68a8d345d7fa07a937fe92fb1fa","tid":2425413,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"你班偽道德撚真係好噁心囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n孟達係劉備最危難時獻上庸降魏<br />\n更直接害死關羽<br />\n然後見勢色唔對就想作反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先叛蜀再反魏 反覆無常<br />\n所以諸葛亮先會設計殺死孟達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再係度同情佢<br />\n呢條柒頭真係係抵佢有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7230e575526a09a66a666e3a6f8c3d5421b925f7","tid":2425413,"uid":117584,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"大愛左膠撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d823f454af2e00d6a97ef968bae1cd775f0124c3","tid":2425413,"uid":52658,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"歷史上好似孟達呢d反覆無常既狡詐之徒<br />\n都唔會有咩好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9736f64842fdbb03ad9a05d4f84ad0d418ac66c2","tid":2425413,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"ddged<br />\n閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06584e3db833bca62f0156fc78de1cc47fb49e9e","tid":2425413,"uid":52658,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌你老母孟達</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98469aff